trans-unit.source: Contains values that specify changes in the structure of the Microsoft UI Automation element tree.
trans-unit.target: Contiene valores que especifican los cambios en la estructura del árbol de elementos de automatización de la interfaz de usuario de Microsoft.

trans-unit.source: A child element was added to the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Se agregó un elemento secundario al árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: A child element was removed from the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Se quitó un elemento secundario del árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Child elements were added to the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Se agregaron elementos secundarios al árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Child elements were removed from the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Se quitaron elementos secundarios del árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Child elements were invalidated in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree.
trans-unit.target: Se invalidaron elementos secundarios en el árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This might mean that one or more children were added or removed, depending on the UI Automation providers implementation.
trans-unit.target: Esto podría significar que uno o más elementos secundarios se agregaron o quitaron, dependiendo de la implementación de proveedores de UI Automation.

trans-unit.source: The order of the child elements in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element tree changed.
trans-unit.target: El orden de los elementos secundarios en el árbol de elementos de [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] ha cambiado.
